transcripts: They may claim good performance, but typically cordless vacuums deliver weak suction. The issue originates here to make their vacuums smaller most others make their motors smaller and less powerful, but at Dyson we've invented the small, but powerful V6 digital motor spinning at up to 110,000 RPM giving our latest cordless vacuums twice the suction of all others.
